Added many features. First needs to be run using Python 3 due to dictionary functions. Secondly must instal django-widget-tweaks using pip.
Added a welcome page called welcome.html and a new catan boardgame called catan.html. Go to localhos:8000/welcome to start a game.
Added bootstrap, jquery, and jquery-ui to make some features of welcome page simple along with modal popups during the actual game.
Added zoom functionality to game by using mousewheel. Also added a pan feature by clicking and dragging.
Made the settlements more house shaped and made a city object that looks more like a city. I also added an outline to these object plus roads that will just pick the same color but darker by 5% using the darken function in background.js
